        <summary> What is the purpose of the doctype declaration?</summary>
        <p>Is an instruction to the web browser about what version of HTML the page is written in.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary>What is the HTML element?</summary>
        <p>The HTML elemnt is an element that contains opening, closing tags and content</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary>What is the purpose of the head element?</summary>
        <p>It provides information about the document itself. It contains meta data.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary> What is the purpose of the body element?</summary>
        <p>In the body element is where all the html structure goes. It is basically where we build the skeleton of a website.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary> How do you create a paragraph in HTML?</summary>
        <p>To create a paragraph we use the p element with angle brackets.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary> How do you create a heading in HTML?</summary>
        <p>To create a heading we can use the h1 element</p>
    </details>
